#

Hearty Vegetable Barley Soup

60 min
$8.99
180 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 6

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianVeganGluten-Free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main Dish

Tags:

SoupHealthyComfort Food

Description

A wholesome and filling soup packed with vegetables and chewy barley, perfect for a cozy meal.

Ingredients

  • vegetable broth: 6 cups
  • barley: 1 cup
  • carrots: 2, diced
  • celery: 2 stalks, diced
  • onion: 1, chopped
  • garlic: 3 cloves, minced
  • potatoes: 2, diced
  • green beans: 1 cup, chopped
  • spinach: 2 cups, fresh
  • salt: to taste
  • pepper: to taste
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • bay leaf: 1
